WEBVTT

00:01.179 --> 00:02.896
<i>Previously on</i> The Vampire Diaries...

00:02.921 --> 00:05.170
BOTH: <i>Incendia.</i>

00:05.172 --> 00:07.205
DAMON: <i>How does an evil siren scheme,</i>

00:07.207 --> 00:08.840
involve three-year-olds?

00:08.842 --> 00:10.465
She wants to offer them to Cade.

00:10.467 --> 00:11.543
DAMON: <i>Who's Cade?</i>

00:11.545 --> 00:12.319
<i>What is he?</i>

00:12.321 --> 00:13.310
He's the devil.

00:13.312 --> 00:15.180
So, you want your freedom

00:15.182 --> 00:17.248
in exchange for these two girls.

00:17.250 --> 00:18.529
Cade, do we have a deal or not?

00:18.531 --> 00:19.851
What if I can offer you

00:19.853 --> 00:21.486
a better one? Two brothers.

00:21.488 --> 00:24.055
Two powerful, immortal vampires.

00:24.057 --> 00:24.889
STEFAN: I'll do it.

00:24.891 --> 00:25.957
Just let the girls go.

00:25.959 --> 00:27.292
<i>I don't know how to protect</i>

00:27.294 --> 00:28.259
my own children.

00:28.261 --> 00:30.028
Yes, you dou Take them

00:30.030 --> 00:31.129
someplace safe.

00:31.131 --> 00:32.564
Take them away from me.

00:32.566 --> 00:33.732
SELINE: <i>I'm done.</i>

00:33.734 --> 00:35.767
No more killing in his name.

00:35.769 --> 00:36.768
Sorry, sissy.

00:36.770 --> 00:37.836
You're about to start

00:37.838 --> 00:38.903
making payments

00:38.905 --> 00:40.438
on your karmic debt.

00:40.440 --> 00:42.640
You cut me out of the agreement?

00:42.642 --> 00:43.775
This is for Tyler.

00:43.777 --> 00:46.344
(Damon grunts)

00:46.346 --> 00:47.887
STEFAN: <i>I surrendered</i>

00:47.889 --> 00:49.748
my immortal soul to Cade.

00:49.750 --> 00:51.716
I have to serve him the
way the sirens did

00:51.718 --> 00:53.318
and deliver the darkest souls to hell

00:53.320 --> 00:54.686
so I don't end up there myself.

00:54.688 --> 00:57.155
My one condition was that
I get to spend my last

00:57.157 --> 00:59.657
24 hours of freedom...

00:59.659 --> 01:01.593
with you.

01:03.730 --> 01:08.199
♪ Silent night ♪

01:08.201 --> 01:12.403
♪ Peaceful night ♪

01:12.405 --> 01:14.806
♪ All things sleep... ♪

01:14.808 --> 01:17.809
(thumping outside)

01:17.811 --> 01:21.646
(gasps) It's him! It's him!

01:21.648 --> 01:24.349
Shh!

01:24.351 --> 01:26.151
He won't come unless you're asleep.

01:26.153 --> 01:30.121
♪ Bethlehem's silent hill ♪

01:30.123 --> 01:32.524
♪ And unseen... ♪

01:32.526 --> 01:35.026
(man grunting)

01:35.028 --> 01:36.528
Isn't he supposed to be on the roof?

01:36.530 --> 01:37.862
We don't have a roof.

01:37.864 --> 01:39.931
(man screams)

01:41.401 --> 01:43.368
(man screaming)

01:43.370 --> 01:45.370
(glass shatters)

01:46.239 --> 01:48.406
(heavy breathing)

01:52.746 --> 01:54.412
I don't think that's Santa.

01:54.414 --> 01:56.648
(exhales)

01:57.957 --> 02:03.732
